{"tid":2258863,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大陸公務員在同事飲水放「母豬發情素」 害女同事狂懷孕、男同事超亢奮","createTime":"2020-10-26T11:08:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-27T23:13:46.000Z","uid":271829,"like":696,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":107,"replies":[{"pid":"1a48ef6a9dee08f04ecb667dfc041e9344202702","tid":2258863,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T11:08:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4594/d4594281.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4594%2Fd4594281.jpg&h=f958d475&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲公務員把母豬交配用的激素加入同事的飲水中，導致多人身體出現異常狀況。（圖／路透社）<br />\n<br />\n山東省乳山市近日傳出一名公務員因不滿人事任用安排，2年半來不斷將刺激母豬發情用的激素，偷加入同事們的飲用水中，導致男同事上班時亢奮不已，女同事接二連三懷孕，還害多名已經停經多年的中年女同事又來了月經。當地警方26日證實此事，表示正在調查中，案件處理完全後會發布通報。<br />\n<br />\n根據網友爆料，該名公務員任職於乳山市統計局，因為對幹部任用的結果不滿意，決定要偷偷報復，於是上網購買了刺激母豬發情用的激素，透過針管注射進統計局平常飲水的水桶中。<br />\n<br />\n爆料指出，該名公務員從2017年8月開始投毒，並持續了兩年半，害統計局內的同事身體出現奇怪的狀況，包含男同事上班時亢奮不已，整天臉色通紅，不停流汗；女同事接二連三的懷孕，經期大亂，甚至還有幾名已停經多年的50多歲女同事又來了月經。<br />\n<br />\n▼疑受到母豬發情激素的影響，統計局內女同事接二連三懷孕，經期大亂。（圖／CFP）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2755/d2755917.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2755%2Fd2755917.jpg&h=5ca6d58f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n除了基層公務員外，統計局的局長李宏飛的身體也出了狀況，脖子腫得跟水桶一樣粗，看起來就像沒有脖子一樣。李宏飛到醫院檢查之後，醫院很快發現他體內的三合激素、丙酸睪丸素、黃體酮等激素嚴重超標，研判是接觸到給母豬催情刺激交配用的藥物。<br />\n<br />\n李宏飛回來之後，把統計局內可能存在激素污染的環節全部檢查了一遍，都沒有找到原因，最後是有人在統計局內部的垃圾桶中，發現了裝動物用激素的玻璃瓶，才追查到投毒的兇手。<br />\n<br />\n由於爆料的內容實在太過離奇，雖然在網路快速瘋傳，但大部分人都沒有當真，認為只是在編造故事，但根據陸媒《瀟湘晨報》報導，乳山市公安局已於26日證實此事，並表示正在調查，案件處理完全會發布通報。"},{"pid":"3e5afbf071cb1c2e8fe0a0269cd6d5bacc627e0b","tid":2258863,"uid":65638,"like":329,"dislike":26,"score":303,"citedBy":12,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T11:10:27.000Z","msg":"邊有可能，豬同人嘅「發情」都唔撚同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 弱智先信"},{"pid":"502ac4c4f0f46ea3f1df64241bf2c308b7142fe7","tid":2258863,"uid":49853,"like":51,"dislike":2,"score":49,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T11:11:16.000Z","msg":"CLS<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2201e997625ec0b8882d0a05f2d8666069b79282","tid":2258863,"uid":65887,"like":295,"dislike":5,"score":290,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T11:13:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://4.share.photo.xuite.net/c828h/149f708/15120563/806219861_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F4.share.photo.xuite.net%2Fc828h%2F149f708%2F15120563%2F806219861_l.jpg&h=dce44fca&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4b3ddfafbef3e03f68d80797d52d2dd28b8042c7","tid":2258863,"uid":104138,"like":323,"dislike":3,"score":320,"quote":{"pid":"3e5afbf071cb1c2e8fe0a0269cd6d5bacc627e0b","tid":2258863,"uid":65638,"like":329,"dislike":26,"score":303,"citedBy":12,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T11:10:27.000Z","msg":"邊有可能，豬同人嘅「發情」都唔撚同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 弱智先信"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T11:13:12.000Z","msg":"因為d 「母豬發情素」 都係假既"},{"pid":"69323ed8ba432cf24043041979e8bfba3f0e6fc9","tid":2258863,"uid":367093,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T11:14:30.000Z","msg":"笑死人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e13542b14b355f87d2d480d9cbc859fb65257ea7","tid":2258863,"uid":11148,"like":193,"dislike":2,"score":191,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T11:14:39.000Z","msg":"由於爆料的內容實在太過離奇，雖然在網路快速瘋傳，但大部分人都沒有當真，認為只是在編造故事<br />\n<br />\n支那比小說更離奇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52b6f980f009093f10de9a0444f7318bc97f4f96","tid":2258863,"uid":70487,"like":52,"dislike":2,"score":50,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T11:15:23.000Z","msg":"返工就係為咗懷孕生下韮菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"604c610a3d0442af23161162481ca02079672632","tid":2258863,"uid":11148,"like":84,"dislike":2,"score":82,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T11:15:56.000Z","msg":"中國人社會之離奇，確是人類社會所罕見。許多文明世界的洋人對發生於中國的慘事往往是半信半疑，起碼也是覺得匪夷所思，不敢盡信，因為情節實在太過離奇，有悖於常理人情，而中國統治者對於這個極有利於中國極權統治的優勢，至今還是懵然不知。中國社會之胡混，以戲劇大師易卜生（Henrik Johan Ibsen 1828－1906）於《群鬼》裡面所述的死人糾纏生人，恐怕尚不足以言其狀，而可能更接近耶魯大學教授Ellsworth Huntington （1876&mdash;1947）所發的驚天之論：「一個人要是沒有這種畸形發展的自私心，也就抵擋不了（中國）那種殘酷的荒年&hellip;&hellip;於是凡是自私自利的心越重，生存的機會就越大；多經一次荒年，人品上自私自利的心理就深一分&hellip;&hellip;總之，極端的自私自利可以使一家人度過荒年，生存下去&hellip;&hellip;二千年的長時間裡，唯有這種自私的人才受選擇。凡是能夠損己利人，解衣推食之輩，在荒年時已經死完了。」<br />\n<br />\n  中國目前的文化，是徹頭徹尾的「為求富貴無所不為」（get-rich-at-any-cost）的文化。不管有多少人認為中國這樣就會好起來了，但我依然深信中國這樣是走邪門，最終並不能提昇中國人的精神文明水準，甚至連物質生活水準也只能在一小撮「人民」裡面有實質提昇，就如歷史學家李弘祺教授說的：像這樣的（中共的）政治經濟體系，在中國運行已經二、三千年，它不是以合理的效益為原則，也不以之為理想。它的運作，一言以蔽之，就是為維護統治機關&hellip;&hellip;讓不合理的、不公平的事情和政策繼續累積，直到它垮掉為止，然後朝代循環，一切重新開始&hellip;&hellip;。」"},{"pid":"1ce532e1be023ae92dad1cf6d26fb31fcfca0946","tid":2258863,"uid":286897,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T11:17:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bff2043944e8afaca9504cbe36bcb9f6825c36ba","tid":2258863,"uid":20867,"like":49,"dislike":7,"score":42,"quote":{"pid":"2201e997625ec0b8882d0a05f2d8666069b79282","tid":2258863,"uid":65887,"like":295,"dislike":5,"score":290,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T11:13:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://4.share.photo.xuite.net/c828h/149f708/15120563/806219861_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F4.share.photo.xuite.net%2Fc828h%2F149f708%2F15120563%2F806219861_l.jpg&h=dce44fca&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T11:19:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64d93019e6c449948a11e0304888802cea8a6222","tid":2258863,"uid":335434,"like":90,"dislike":1,"score":89,"quote":{"pid":"3e5afbf071cb1c2e8fe0a0269cd6d5bacc627e0b","tid":2258863,"uid":65638,"like":329,"dislike":26,"score":303,"citedBy":12,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T11:10:27.000Z","msg":"邊有可能，豬同人嘅「發情」都唔撚同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 弱智先信"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T11:20:02.000Z","msg":"因為支国公務員都係豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be87797e8516ec2c82297010b9ac435ccb380c89","tid":2258863,"uid":155818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T11:20:47.000Z","msg":"哈哈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6617b152a3c7a396a35c252a1a938f872c1ed6f5","tid":2258863,"uid":61105,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T11:20:52.000Z","msg":"唔知點解笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6887e3bd3de73b7a10b684734836112ab35a814","tid":2258863,"uid":21634,"like":119,"dislike":3,"score":116,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T11:23:39.000Z","msg":"成班員工返工就係瘋狂做愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n淫亂辦公室<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成地都係精液閪汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d08e9a6ca874e441081998778efbd132f29687d6","tid":2258863,"uid":168366,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T11:24:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b486f3a5194dce048385fefbfd9b5aeb6b1de480","tid":2258863,"uid":274732,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T11:27:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nCls"},{"pid":"b08008d07a53603d193ec67a517dd94fd61358d5","tid":2258863,"uid":7323,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T11:28:21.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\