這樣是走邪門，最終並不能提昇中國人的精神文明水準，甚至連物質生活水準也只能在一小撮「人民」裡面有實質提昇，就如歷史學家李弘祺教授說的：像這樣的（中共的）政治經濟體系，在中國運行已經二、三千年，它不是以合理的效益為原則，也不以之為理想。它的運作，一言以蔽之，就是為維護統治機關&hellip;&hellip;讓不合理的、不公平的事情和政策繼續累積，直到它垮掉為止，然後朝代循環，一切重新開始&hellip;&hellip;。」"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T11:50:01.000Z","msg":"50年代已經睇穿。cls"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T12:59:04.000Z","msg":"鍾祖康1960年先出世喎"},{"pid":"58fdd36784fa4624cc2b745b12ff98aaef1e5a51","tid":2258863,"uid":296589,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T13:01:27.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">屌<strong>閪</strong>梗係懷孕喇 白9痴</span>"},{"pid":"5d964d8c130b98f9776f691fac99dbe1658ad2bb","tid":2258863,"uid":13067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T13:01:49.000Z","msg":"笑死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />push"},{"pid":"75ddf2484d4a42c48128e5fadbc371370b50840f","tid":2258863,"uid":258106,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"52b6f980f009093f10de9a0444f7318bc97f4f96","tid":2258863,"uid":70487,"like":52,"dislike":2,"score":50,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T11:15:23.000Z","msg":"返工就係為咗懷孕生下韮菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T13:07:22.000Z","msg":"成件事好社會主義<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a4137176a60763ffea2366b206d753d30010cd9","tid":2258863,"uid":307398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T13:12:17.000Z","msg":"呢d係支那人先諗得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/unwell.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/unwell.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/unwell.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3687a82584c1c7b4c7ace834dc828cf69c8d2611","tid":2258863,"uid":255637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T13:12:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma